      "content": "that makes sense. so when i'm writing the section where i debunk the meritocracy stuff, should i just call it an outdated or flawed concept? it feels like the argument they use is basically just ignoring the facts of systemic racism. how do i write that so it sounds like their position is fundamentally incorrect rather than just a different opinion?",
